---
import { Image } from "astro:assets";
import bgimage from "../assets/images/awkward2.png";
---

<section class="max-w-7xl mx-auto py-12 md:py-16 px-4 md:px-16">
  <h2 class="font-montserrat text-heading2 font-extrabold tracking-tighter pb-4 text-firstkiss-500 max-w-2xl animationinviewfade">here’s how it actually works.</h2>
  <p class="max-w-2xl text-pretty pb-12 text-pillowtalk-500 animationinviewfade">making plans with friends (and meeting new ones) shouldn’t be hard. with Doubble Events, it’s as easy as picking an event, choosing your crew, and showing up.</p>
  <article class="bg-[url('../assets/images/awkward2.png')] bg-cover bg-center h-auto py-16 rounded-3xl">
    <div class="bg-greenflag-500 max-w-md rounded-3xl px-10 py-8">
      <h3 class="text-heading4 font-extrabold text-afterhours-500 pb-4">explore events nearby</h3>
      <p>scroll through what's happening this weekend. disco night? chess & cocktails? you’re in.</p>
    </div>
  </article>
</section>
